body_individualsFinish:
Hello,

Thank you for using our service!

We have received your appraisal. Your file number is: %{reference}.

What's next now?

  • A member of our team will get back to you within the next business day with a firm purchase offer, valid for 48 hours.

  • If you accept our offer, we will set an appointment for you to drop-off your car at one of our dealerships or for a home pick-up.

  • Our team member will ensure that the information you have provided in the appraisal is OK. Once the information is verified, we will buy your car! In case of discrepancies between the actual condition of the car and your appraisal, an adjustment of the price will be calculated and a revised offer will be made to you.

  • We will handle all paperwork for you.

  • You will receive your payment per secure irrevocable wire transfer within 48 working hours.

Any question? We are available for you Monday through Saturday, from 9am to 6pm.

Phone: %{phone}
Email : %{email}

Your autobiz team
